		<Row Tag="LOC_CIVILIZATION_ILLUMINATI_NAME">
			<Text>Illuminati</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_CIVILIZATION_ILLUMINATI_FULLNAME">
			<Text>The Order of the Illuminati</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_CIVILIZATION_ILLUMINATI_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A secret society of immense power and influence, the Illuminati operate from the shadows. Keepers of ancient relics including the legendary Ark of the Covenant.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_MOD_CODE_OF_LAWS_REVEAL_CIV_CULTURE_TREE_ILLUMINATI_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Illuminati Antiquity Age Civilization</Text>
		</Row>

