			<Gender>Neuter</Gender>
		</Row>

		<!-- Ability-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_ILLUMINATI_ABILITY_NAME">
			<Text>Keepers of the Ark</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_ILLUMINATI_ABILITY_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>[LIST][LI][B]+3[icon:YIELD_GOLD] Gold[/B] in all cities.[LI][B]+2[icon:YIELD_DIPLOMACY] Influence[/B] in all cities (Shadow Network).[LI]Unique Culture Tree: [B]Illuminati Traditions[/B] with powerful bonuses.[LI]Unique Wonder: [B]Eye of Providence[/B] (+2 Culture, +2 Gold, +3 Influence).[LI]Unique Building: [B]Secret Lodge[/B] (+2 Gold, +1 Culture).[LI]Unique Units: [B]Knights Templar[/B] (elite cavalry) and [B]Assassin[/B] (17 Combat, +5 at full health, +30 vs Commanders).[/LIST]</Text>
		</Row>

